  "projectName": "Proyecto1cc7 — Bare-Metal ARM OS",
  "projectDescription": "A bare-metal preemptive operating system for ARM Cortex-A8 (BeagleBone Black / QEMU) featuring a round-robin scheduler, IRQ-driven context switching, and a minimal standard library.",
